<i>from the Japanese government.</i>

125
00:08:50.296 --> 00:08:52.965  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>Are our demands unreasonable?</i>

126
00:08:53.633 --> 00:08:54.867  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>That's not the case.</i>

127
00:08:54.934 --> 00:08:59.672  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>As Ajin, we just want</i>
<i>our most basic requests to be granted.</i>

128
00:09:00.640 --> 00:09:04.710  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>We want formal and detailed</i>
<i>public disclosure of the experiments</i>

129
00:09:04.777 --> 00:09:08.548  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>performed on Ajin by the government</i>
<i>and affiliated industries,</i>

130
00:09:08.848 --> 00:09:14.320  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>as well as the profits</i>
<i>obtained from those experiments,</i>

131
00:09:14.587 --> 00:09:17.023  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
