<i>to be recognized.</i>

132
00:09:17.089 --> 00:09:18.724  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
<i>Those are our two demands.</i>

133
00:09:18.791 --> 00:09:24.964  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
